Suva is the capital of Fiji, a busy harbor city featuring a beautiful mix of modern buildings and traditional colonial architecture, framed by natural beauty all around. Its also the location of Vodafone Arena, where Pastor Doug has just preached to thousands about finding the keys to Gods eternal kingdom.
